---
layout: base.njk
title: Contact Stuart Gilbert Landrovers | Land Rover Specialist, Sittingbourne
metaDescription: Contact our independent Land Rover workshop in Sittingbourne, Kent. Call 01795 843116 to book, or send a message. Orchards, Sittingbourne, ME9 8JX.
permalink: /contact/
turnstile: true
preloadFonts:
  - /fonts/fraunces-latin-var.woff2
---
<section class="contact">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head">
      <div class="tag">Contact</div>
      <h2>Get in touch with the workshop.</h2>
      <p>A telephone call is by far the quickest way to reach us. You'll get Stuart or David, and we can book your Land Rover straight in. If you'd rather drop us a message, use the form below and we'll get back to you.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-grid">
      <div class="contact-primary">
        <a class="contact-phone" href="tel:{{ site.phoneTel }}">
          <small>Call the workshop</small>
          <span class="number">{{ site.phoneDisplay }}</span>
        </a>
        <div class="contact-hours">
          <h3>Opening hours</h3>
          <p>{{ site.hours.days }}<br>{{ site.hours.short }}<br>By appointment only</p>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-addr">
          <h3>Workshop</h3>
          <address>{{ site.address.street }}<br>{{ site.address.locality }}<br>{{ site.address.region }} {{ site.address.postcode }}</address>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-form-wrap">
        {% if basePath %}<p class="preview-note">This is a preview of the new site. The message form isn't connected yet, so please call <a href="tel:{{ site.phoneTel }}">{{ site.phoneDisplay }}</a> for now.</p>{% endif %}
        <form class="contact-form" method="POST" action="/api/contact">
          <p class="form-row">
            <label for="name">Your name</label>
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" autocomplete="name" required>
          </p>
          <p class="form-row">
            <label for="contact">Phone number or email</label>
            <input type="text" id="contact" name="contact" autocomplete="tel" required>
          </p>
          <p class="form-row">
            <label for="message">How can we help?</label>
            <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" required></textarea>
          </p>
          <p class="hp" aria-hidden="true">
            <label for="company">Company</label>
            <input type="text" id="company" name="company" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off">
          </p>
          <div class="cf-turnstile" data-sitekey="TURNSTILE_SITE_KEY_PLACEHOLDER"></div>
          <p id="ts-status" role="status" class="ts-status"></p>
          <button type="submit" class="btn-submit">Send message</button>
          <p class="form-note">Prefer to talk? Call <a href="tel:{{ site.phoneTel }}">{{ site.phoneDisplay }}</a>. It's the fastest way to reach us.</p>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="area area-contact">
  <div class="contours" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div>
      <div class="section-head" style="margin-bottom:0">
        <div class="tag">Find us</div>
        <h2>Orchards, Sittingbourne.</h2>
        <p style="color:var(--hero-mute)">We're a short drive from most of mid Kent. The workshop is by appointment only, so please call before setting off.</p>
      </div>
      <address>
        <b>{{ site.name }}</b>
        {{ site.address.street }}, {{ site.address.locality }}, {{ site.address.region }} {{ site.address.postcode }}<br>
        {{ site.hours.display }}
      </address>
    </div>
    {% include "partials/map.njk" %}
  </div>
</section>
